Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.51,1:28:42.61,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,选上了你们呐
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.45,1:28:52.42,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再多进攻些
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.70,1:29:07.50,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.01,1:29:09.87,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再多...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.31,1:29:12.24,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使出些全部力量!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.01,1:29:45.95,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和这个贝卡大人我对战
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.95,1:29:47.64,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然能占到一瞬间的上风
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.38,1:29:50.61,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个叫隆的男人...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.65,1:29:53.05,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝卡!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.32,1:29:59.12,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯 现在!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.19,1:30:01.93,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龙卷旋风腿!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.93,1:30:03.62,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,升龙拳!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.50,1:30:08.62,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收下了!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.17,1:30:10.83,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦!
