Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.32,1:32:43.72,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春丽!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.86,1:32:51.38,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春丽...
