Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.55,1:33:19.11,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像约定的那样 我好好替你报仇了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.53,1:33:24.02,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.00,1:33:27.25,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在美军协助下
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.25,1:33:30.63,BLC-45,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国际刑警组织成功的摧毁了Shadowlaw组织
